    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>G. Claude Drake was president of the Quary Drugstore in Ann Arbor, Michigan.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The Drake collection consists of manuscripts and photographs largely relating to the Quarry drugstore in Ann Arbor, Michigan. Of interest are photographs of Quarry Drugstore, University of Michigan campus and buildings, a 1908 football game, and the Huron River.</p>
    </scopecontent>
